column1: #text=Being pregnant with my first child all I ever craved was chocolate cake .
#text=Every time I went outside I had to find somewhere to buy one .
#text=I was truly a chocolate cake addict but had no clue how to bake a cake .
#text=I decided to buy one from the supermarket out of the box .
#text=The recipe called for me to have water , oil and eggs which I had at home .
#text=In a rush I quickly read the directions and preheat my oven to 350 degrees .
#text=I poured the eggs , water , oil and cake mix in the box and beat it with my hand blender for about a minute .
#text=The smell of the gooey chocolate in the bowl make my little bundle of joy inside me kick for joy .
#text=When I was pouring it into the pan to bake it was hard to resist temptation of a taste .
#text=But knowing that raw eggs are unhealthy I decided to to the twenty five minutes until it was done .
#text=When my timer went off I removed it from the oven and tried a small piece .
#text=It was one of the most moist and delicious cakes I ever had .
